{"tid":2375493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩人事隔超過一年被控紅磡參與暴動 其中一人保釋申請被拒","createTime":"2021-01-22T05:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T16:38:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"56208f69b61edc27be629949f9c9dc5dc4eaecbb","tid":2375493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13153&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=705877f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13153</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 <br />\n#1201黃埔 #新案件<br />\n<br />\nD1: 何 (23)<br />\nD2: 鍾 (25)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：暴動 [D1-2]<br />\n被控於2019年12月1日在紅磡德康街、德安街及船景街附近一帶與陳及其他身份不詳的人士參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n當日在九龍有一個「毋忘初心大遊行」，晚上8時，有示威者在黃埔一帶放火堵路，警方到場掃蕩。警員X目睹D2手持磚頭放到地上。<br />\n<br />\n控方為案中所有警員申請匿名令，裁判官照准。<br />\n<br />\n２名被告毋須答辯，控方打算將案件轉介至區域法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年2月19日1430在九龍城裁判法院第一庭再訊<br />\n<br />\n📌#保釋事宜<br />\n<br />\n✅D1獲准保釋，條件如下：<br />\n&bull; $50,000現金<br />\n&bull; 不得離港，交出旅遊證件<br />\n&bull; 每日報到<br />\n<br />\n❌D2保釋申請遭拒❌"},{"pid":"25be4d0967a3d137476afa1a70e12a3c038849d5","tid":2375493,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cf9655bd79c80423e73e96cfd60d8894072bb4","tid":2375493,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b72081ee5b870506fd818eafabe3fd324074cac","tid":2375493,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/